{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"73c083d350","title":"在中央给张经武的电报稿上加写的一段话","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"d3d0df68ad","index":0,"year":1951,"month":11,"day":14,"articleId":"73c083d350"}],"tags":[{"id":"d5cbd05390","name":"通讯","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji31","name":"毛泽东全集第31卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/31-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji31":{"comments":[{"id":"c011c30dec","publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"73c083d350","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"张经武，当时任中央人民政府驻西藏代表。"},{"id":"07b8a46bfb","publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"73c083d350","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指西藏宗教领袖达赖喇嘛·丹增嘉措准备向毛泽东等中央领导人送礼物一事。中央在给张经武的电报中，指示了对这一问题的处理意见：“只要送毛主席一份礼物即够，且礼物不要多。锦旗外，送什么东西，由他们决定。但除供陈列的文物外，土产和用品都不要送（都是取之于民的东西），或尽少送。此外，向朱总司令、周总理送一面锦旗，对其他负责人均不要送。”"},{"id":"76fbabce99","publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"73c083d350","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"国华，即张国华，当时任驻西藏的中国人民解放军第十八军军长。"}],"contents":[{"id":"1b1116e92d","type":"title","text":"在中央给张经武\"的电报稳上加写的一段话","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"73c083d350"},{"id":"c011c30dec","type":"paragraph","text":"因达赖送礼事与你回中央一事有关，但中央认为你暂时应留拉萨帮助国华等工作一个时期，何时回来将来再定，因此达赖送礼事亦应缓办。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"73c083d350"}],"page":{"id":"724e0c19ff","publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"73c083d350","start":65,"end":65}}}},"__N_SSG":true}